file_content.text: Strike, Drinda-Zel! Bring honor to Emperor Malgus!
I am Chieftain Velasu Graege, uniter of the Kaleesh tribes and destroyer of the Republic!
I am Chieftain Velasu Graege, uniter of the Kaleesh tribes and bane of the old Empire!
Malgus will honor me for your death!
What trophy will I claim from you? An ear? Your weapons?
